in the Comfy plan</h2></div><div><!--[--><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Machine Setup</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Comfy Cloud runs on Blackwell RTX 6000 Pro – 96GB VRAM</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Time limit per job</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">On our Standard and Creator plans, each workflow has a maximum run time of 30 minutes. On the Pro plan, the limit is increased to 1 hour. Jobs exceeding that limit are automatically cancelled to ensure fair usage and system stability.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Usage</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">You're only charged for <strong>active GPU</strong> time while a workflow is running. Idle time (e.g. time spent building workflows) does not consume GPU hours.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Credit balance</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">All plans will include a monthly pool of credits that are spent on active workflow runtime and <a href="https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/partner-nodes/overview" class="text-primary-comfy-yellow underline">Partner Nodes</a> like Nano Banana Pro.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Add more credits anytime</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Purchase additional credits at any time. Unused top-ups roll over to the next month automatically for up to 1 year.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Pre-installed models</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Access a library of 900+ pre-installed models.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Custom nodes support</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Comfy Cloud currently supports a variety of the most-used custom nodes from the ComfyUI community. We're expanding support regularly based on demand and compatibility.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Partner Nodes</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Run <strong>proprietary models</strong> through Comfy's <a href="https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/partner-nodes/overview" class="text-primary-comfy-yellow underline">Partner Nodes</a>, such as Nano Banana. The amount of credits each node uses depends on the model and parameters you set in the node, but these credits are the same ones that your monthly subscription comes with. These credits can also be used across Comfy Cloud and local ComfyUI. Read more about Partner nodes <a href="https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/partner-nodes/overview" class="text-primary-comfy-yellow underline">here</a>.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Job queue</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Queue up to 100 workflows at once.</p></div><div class="border-primary-comfy-canvas/15 border-b border-solid py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/check.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Custom LoRA importing</p><!----></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">For those on the Creator or Pro plans, you can bring in your own models & LoRAs from CivitAI or Huggingface to perfect your own style.</p></div><div class="py-8 first:pt-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] lg:gap-x-10"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><img src="/icons/clock.svg" alt="" class="mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas text-sm font-medium">Parallel job execution</p><span class="text-primary-comfy-yellow mt-1 inline-block text-xs">coming soon</span></div></div><p class="text-primary-comfy-canvas/55 mt-3 text-sm/relaxed lg:mt-0">Run multiple workflows in parallel to speed up your pipeline.</p></div><!--]--></div></div></section>  </main> <astro-island uid="ZTWRtB" prefix="s3" component-url="/_website/SiteFooter.gihjwwuG.js" component-export="default" renderer-url="/_website/client.7Oa-x_ju.js" props="{&quot;locale&quot;:[0,&quot;en&quot;]}" ssr client="load" opts="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SiteFooter&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}" await-children><footer class="bg-primary-comfy-ink text-primary-comfy-canvas px-6 py-8 lg:px-20"><div class="border-primary-warm-gray grid gap-12 border-t pt-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-4"><p class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-wide uppercase lg:text-3xl">The most powerful workflow engine for visual AI.</p><div class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:row-span-2 lg:justify-between"><div class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:hidden"><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12"><!--[--><nav aria-label="Products" class="flex flex-col gap-4"><h3 class="text-sm font-bold">Products</h3><div class="flex flex-col"><!--[--><a href="/download" class="hover:text-primary-warm-white block py-1.5 text-sm transition-colors">Comfy Local <!----></a><a href="/cloud" class="hover:text-primary-warm-white block py-1.5 text-sm transition-colors">Comfy Cloud <!----></a><a href="/api" class="hover:text-primary-warm-white block py-1.5 text-sm transition-colors">Comfy API <!----></a><a href="/cloud/enterprise" class="hover:text-primary-warm-white block py-1.5 text-sm transition